\fs24 \cf3 \super 11\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub Jesus entered Jerusalem and went into the temple courts. He looked around at everything, but since it was already late, he went out to Bethany with the Twelve.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus looks around and says \'96 It starts tomorrow.\
