\fs24 \cf3 \super 12\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub The next day as they were leaving Bethany, Jesus was hungry.\'a0
\f4\b \super 13\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub Seeing in the distance a fig tree in leaf, he went to find out if it had any fruit.  When he reached it, he found nothing but leaves, because it was not the season for figs.\'a0
\f4\b \super 14\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub Then he said to the tree,\'a0\'93May no one ever eat fruit from you again.\'94\'a0And his disciples heard him say it.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is not the normal story you hear preached of Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus \'96 the tree killer \'96 staring\'85Jesus of Nazareth.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We don\'92t hear this version of Him much\'85but then the story gets even more odd\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But then it goes on\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf3 \super 15\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub On reaching Jerusalem, Jesus entered the temple courts and began driving out those who were buying and selling there. \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In one version it says he makes a whip!  He goes all Indiana jones on them!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 He overturned the tables of the money changers and the benches of those selling doves,
\f4\b \super 16\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub and would not allow anyone to carry merchandise through the temple courts.\'a0
\f4\b \super 17\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub And as he taught them, he said,\'a0\'93Is it not written: \'91My house will be called a house of prayer for all nations\'92
\f4\b \super [\ul c\ulnone ]
\f5\b0 \nosupersub ?\'a0But you have made it \'91a den of robbers.\'92
\f4\b \super [\ul d\ulnone ]
\f5\b0 \nosupersub \'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus comes in and just overthrows everything.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And He\'92s mad not because they are selling things\'85but because they are ripping people off.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ve heard some people say you shouldn\'92t sell anything in the church because of this passage\'85that isn\'92t the point.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The point is they would sell doves and animals needed for sacrifice at an incredibly inflated rate because people would travel very far and have no other way to get stuff.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were like local movie theaters \'96 when you go up and order a small popcorn and small drink it\'92s like $47.50!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You know you could get a big gulp at a 7-11 for like 89 cents but in the movie theater\'85it\'92s $15!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is what was happening here\'85this was the problem.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There was some seriously bad things happening inside the temple of God.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf3 \super 18\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub The chief priests and the teachers of the law heard this and began looking for a way to kill him, for they feared him,\'a0because the whole crowd was amazed at his teaching.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And here is the tension:  In their minds Jesus went to the wrong place.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They didn\'92t need help in the temple, they needed help with the Roman soldiers who were oppressing them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But just like so often when dealing with Jesus, what He wants to rule over isn\'92t what they wanted Him to rule over.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This happens all the times in our lives doesn\'92t it?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf3 \super 16\'a0
\f5\b0 \cf3 \nosupersub Don\'92t you know that you yourselves are God\'92s temple\'a0and that God\'92s Spirit dwells in your midst?\'a0  1 Cor 3\
\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want God to deal with our circumstances not our hearts!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God fix my \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Marriage or spouse \'96 don\'92t deal with me\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Fix my job not my attitude\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Fix them\'85I\'92m fine!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li2160\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question \'96 If you\'92re a Christian have you made Jesus king of your circumstances or your heart?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God may be waiting to change your circumstances until you allow Him to change your heart because He knows you handle better circumstances until your heart becomes whole.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f5\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your circumstances are not what Jesus came to earth to save you from\'85it is yourself!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
