\ls11\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Let\'92s not miss that we celebrate what happened \'96 but also what is happening\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Easter is a week away \'96 we will celebrate what happened that changed the whole world in an instant\'85but we need to make sure this week we prepare our own hearts and make sure we are allowing Him to come in and not just rule over circumstances but also our hearts.\
