\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Crazy day \'96 it started with Jesus crusing a fig tree and then went into throwing all the religious leaders out of the temple\'85it culminates in the next two lines.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf3 \super 20\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub In the morning, as they went along, they saw the fig tree withered from the roots.\'a0
\f4\b \super 21\'a0
\f5\b0 \nosupersub Peter remembered and said to Jesus, \'93Rabbi,\'a0look! The fig tree you cursed has withered!\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
\f3 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus not only cursed it\'85He killed it!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here\'92s why though\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}First off, the fig tree is the national symbol of Israel.  I don\'92t know why they chose a tree but they did.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So Jesus walks up to this tree that represents the nation of Israel and finds nothing of any value on it.  It is suppose to provide life and nourishment for all who see it but it doesn\'92t.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But wasn\'92t it suppose to be out of season?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Yes, but when they have green leaves they are suppose to have fruit.  The leaves are there to show this tree is giving away life in the form of fruit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When Jesus see\'92s it far off he assumes because of the leaves it should naturally have fruit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You see, if a tree looks like it has life to give but doesn\'92t that is false advertising.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus looks at the tree that represents Israel and says you are suppose to be life and hope for the whole world\'85but you only appear to have life.  You\'92ve become false advertisement.  When people show up to worship me they aren\'92t given hope and life they are robbed and walk away still hungry for God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So he curses and removes it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 The Church\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}False advertising \'96 there are a lot of churches that look like this right?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus said the tree looked good from a far but once you go up to eat of it, there is nothing there.  There was nothing to eat.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Maybe you\'92ve been to a church like that.  Where from far there seems to be a lot of activity, but once you got closer to it you realized it was just a lot of motion but no real life change.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why we are starting a new church.  It\'92s not because we looked around and decided there were no churches in town\'85it\'92s because we realized there were large groups of people who were walking away from God and \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
