\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 Stats to use:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It would be easy for me to talk about the over 4,000 churches that close their doors every year and the countless more that are so small they actually a small group that meets in a church.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It would be easy for me to talk about he 2.7 million church members who fall into inactivity every year!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It would be easy to talk about how the United States now ranks 3\super rd\nosupersub  following only China and India in the number of people who are not professing Christians.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It would be easy to talk about how half of all church didn\'92t add a single member in the last two years.\
